00:00:33.980 --> 00:00:38.800
scientific underpinnings are both at an individual
level and an organizational level in terms

00:00:38.800 --> 00:00:42.590
of fostering creativity, what are some of
the blocks and what are some of the enablers

00:00:42.590 --> 00:00:43.590
