00:20:08.440 --> 00:20:09.859
which is not the fun way.

00:20:09.859 --> 00:20:13.590
If you're trying to figure out who's most
likely to become a U.S. army ranger, it's

00:20:13.590 --> 00:20:15.149
the ones with the highest levels of grit.

00:20:15.149 --> 00:20:19.159
Which amateur golfers are most likely to make
