00:20:22.720 --> 00:20:24.230
the highest levels of grit.

00:20:24.230 --> 00:20:26.929
Which teachers are mostly likely to make it
through an intercity school for the first

00:20:26.929 --> 00:20:29.149
year, the ones with the highest levels of
grit?

00:20:29.149 --> 00:20:32.440
Which graduates of Wharton Business School
are gonna make the most money 3 years from

00:20:32.440 --> 00:20:33.440
now.

00:20:33.440 --> 00:20:34.760
The ones with the highest levels of grit.

00:20:34.760 --> 00:20:40.330
That in field after field, grit explains,
