00:20:47.460 --> 00:20:53.539
domains and that's because creativity by definition
in the 21st century is gonna be hard.

00:20:53.539 --> 00:20:57.380
If it were easy that product would already
exist, that patent would have been filed,

00:20:57.380 --> 00:20:58.600
that poem would have been written.

00:20:58.600 --> 00:21:03.940
So it's always gonna involve lots of frustration,
