00:21:27.090 --> 00:21:33.159
well, grit is what allows you to show up again
and again.

00:21:33.159 --> 00:21:38.299
So far I've been attempting to describe these
two distinct forms of creativity which depend

00:21:38.299 --> 00:21:41.850
on very distinct patterns of activity in the
brain.

00:21:41.850 --> 00:21:45.789
The more practical lesson though, is that
different kinds of creative problems benefit

00:21:45.789 --> 00:21:48.009
from different kinds of creative thinking.

00:21:48.009 --> 00:21:52.110
The question, of course, is how do we adjust
our thought process to the task at hand?

00:21:52.110 --> 00:21:53.999
When should we daydream and take warm showers?

00:21:53.999 --> 00:21:57.010
And when should we drink another cup of coffee?

00:21:57.010 --> 00:22:02.690
What requires relaxation and what requires
grit?

00:22:02.690 --> 00:22:08.269
The good news, and this is very good news,
