00:24:00.999 --> 00:24:03.049
If I go right, I'm going a little further
away."

00:24:03.049 --> 00:24:08.139
We're able to measure progress towards a destination
when we don't know what the destination is.

00:24:08.139 --> 00:24:13.099
Now, I think we can use these feelings of
knowing to help us diagnose our creative problems,

00:24:13.099 --> 00:24:17.770
then figure out, you know, should we drink
